"end","s":228.94,"e":229,"line":56},{"w":"of","s":229,"e":229.24,"line":56},{"w":"the","s":229.24,"e":229.48,"line":56},{"w":"ground.","s":229.48,"e":230.06,"line":56}],"lines":[{"s":2.8,"e":7.32,"text":"Lord, look at the Earth."},{"s":9.76,"e":13.44,"text":"Look at the smoke, the blood, the oceans, the children."},{"s":14.74,"e":16.44,"text":"We were handed a garden,"},{"s":16.44,"e":19.44,"text":"and we built a battlefield."},{"s":20.26,"e":26.9,"text":"So let this be the warning before the mercy runs out."},{"s":27.72,"e":33.06,"text":"Twenty-four to seventy-two months, we gotta turn this around,"},{"s":34.54,"e":40.44,"text":"No more war in the sky, no more poison in the ground."},{"s":41.52,"e":47.96,"text":"No more hate in the house, no more kings with a crown,"},{"s":49.28,"e":54.78,"text":"If Heaven calls the fire, who can hold it back now?"},{"s":54.78,"e":58.94,"text":"Put our foot down, put our hands up,"},{"s":59.4,"e":62.5,"text":"Clean the air, heal the land, let the guns rust."},{"s":62.78,"e":65.8,"text":"God and the people gotta move right now,"},{"s":65.8,"e":69.56,"text":"Before the whole world trembles at the weight of the crown."},{"s":69.62,"e":72.86,"text":"I saw an asteroid shining like judgment in orbit,"},{"s":73.96,"e":76.58,"text":"Texas-sized shadow where the proud tried to ignore it."},{"s":76.64,"e":78.44,"text":"Not a weapon in my hand, but a mirror in the sky,"},{"s":78.58,"e":80.42,"text":"Showing every nation what it costs when love dies."},{"s":80.56,"e":82.16,"text":"Smoke in the lungs of the babies in the city,"},{"s":82.4,"e":83.92,"text":"Blood in the dust while the powerful look pretty."},{"s":83.92,"e":85.82,"text":"Greed got a throne, hate got a sound,"},{"s":85.86,"e":87.8,"text":"But the meek still whisper, “Lord, turn it around.”"},{"s":87.9,"e":89.88,"text":"This ain’t revenge, this is warning."},{"s":90.1,"e":91.74,"text":"This ain’t wrath, this is mourning."},{"s":91.84,"e":93.66,"text":"The clock keeps burning, the seas keep rising,"},{"s":93.72,"e":96.26,"text":"But mercy is still on the horizon."},{"s":96.78,"e":102.64,"text":"Twenty-four to seventy-two months, we gotta turn this around,"},{"s":103.98,"e":110,"text":"No more war in the sky, no more poison in the ground."},{"s":110,"e":118.26,"text":"No more hate in the house, no more kings with a crown,"},{"s":119.16,"e":124.76,"text":"If Heaven calls the fire, who can hold it back now?"},{"s":125.62,"e":128.98,"text":"Put our foot down, put our hands up,"},{"s":129.34,"e":132.46,"text":"Clean the air, heal the land, let the guns rust."},{"s":132.46,"e":135.72,"text":"God and the people gotta move right now,"},{"s":135.72,"e":139.78,"text":"Before the whole world trembles at the weight of the crown."},{"s":141.34,"e":144.52,"text":"Ohhh, don’t let the garden die,"},{"s":145.02,"e":147.44,"text":"Don’t let another mother cry."},{"s":147.82,"e":151.52,"text":"If we still got breath, we still got time,"},{"s":151.52,"e":155,"text":"But we can’t keep wasting divine signs."},{"s":155.02,"e":156.82,"text":"Every race, every creed, every prayer, every name,"},{"s":157.06,"e":158.68,"text":"Different roads to the light, same tears in the rain."},{"s":158.72,"e":160.54,"text":"If your God is love, then prove it with peace,"},{"s":160.56,"e":162.38,"text":"If your faith is truth, let the violence cease."},{"s":162.38,"e":164.18,"text":"Turn missiles into metal for bridges and trains,"},{"s":164.18,"e":166.08,"text":"Turn factories clean, wash the poison from drains."},{"s":166.08,"e":167.9,"text":"Feed every child, give the homeless a door,"},{"s":168.24,"e":169.94,"text":"Make Earth holy like it was before."},{"s":171.89,"e":175.52,"text":"The crown ain’t for conquest, the crown is a choice,"},{"s":175.78,"e":179.26,"text":"A cosmic alarm with a thunderous voice."},{"s":179.72,"e":182.86,"text":"Either we heal, or we learn too late"},{"s":182.86,"e":187.82,"text":"That no empire survives when it worships hate."},{"s":188.02,"e":193.82,"text":"Twenty-four to seventy-two months, we gotta turn this around,"},{"s":194.72,"e":200.46,"text":"No more war in the sky, no more poison in the ground."},{"s":201.36,"e":208.52,"text":"No more hate in the house, no more kings with a crown,"},{"s":209.74,"e":215.24,"text":"Lord, restore the order, bring the mercy down."},{"s":215.32,"e":219.36,"text":"Put our foot down, put our hands up,"},{"s":219.36,"e":222.92,"text":"Clean the air, heal the land, let the guns rust."},{"s":223.04,"e":226.16,"text":"God and the people gotta move right now,"},{"s":226.48,"e":230.06,"text":"Let the crown be a warning, not the end of the ground."}],"duration":232.12,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-30T01:57:12.497Z","stats":{"whisperWords":523,"polishedWords":519,"matched":490,"matchRate":0.944}}